high_descs: Turn left and move to the end of the counter in front of the two yellow chairs.
Pick up the blue handled ladle to the left of the gray mug from the counter.
Turn right and move to the sink to the left of the coffee maker and in front of the window .
Place the ladle in the sink in front of the knife, rinse the ladle with water from the faucet, then pick up the ladle from the sink.
Move to the right and face the gray coffee maker between the sink and the blue toaster.
Place the ladle in front of the coffee maker near the edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed ladle on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the white kitchen counter and face it so that the yellow chairs are to your left.
Pick the ladle with the blue handle up from the counter.
With the ladle in hand, go over to face the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink, wash it, and then pick it up from in the sink again.
Bring the ladle a step to the right and turn left to face the coffee machine on the left side of the sink.
Put the ladle down in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Move a clean ladle to the counter in front of the coffee.

high_descs: Take a step to your left then walk to the counter and turn right to face it.
Pick up the ice cream scoop that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the sink that's on your left.
Wash the scoop in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Take a step to your right.
Put the scoop in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ice cream scoop on the counter.
